--- !u!114 &3110303637909082364
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 386812503373511526}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7382ee6825142cd43aa3754d7c7b55df, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialWriting
  sentenceText: {fileID: 3738428415428332185}
  sentences:
  - Mouse Wheel Up - Move Right  &  Mouse Wheel Down - Move Left  &  Click Mouse
    Wheel button to stop player Movement
  - For movement you can use A  &  D as well for easy movement
  - Space - Jump   and   You can do wall jumps as well between two walls in Parallel
  - R - Restart If you are stuck somewhere
  - E - Change the worlds   also   In the Inverted World there will be an Orb chasing
    you
  - Each level will have hint timer of 60 seconds after taht you can press H to get
    a hint to clear the level
  pauseGameWhileShowing: 1
